sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant IdP as Auth Service
    participant Redis as Revocation Store
    participant API as API Instance
    participant Att as Attacker

    User->>IdP: Logout / revoke session
    IdP->>Redis: revoked(jti)=true
    Att->>API: Replay old token
    API-->>Att: Allowed during stale window
    API->>Redis: Refresh/check revocation
    API-->>Att: Rejected after convergence